343
00:19:16,540 --> 00:19:17,320
Erduo, come here.

344
00:19:20,250 --> 00:19:20,940
Don't worry about it.

345
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:23,480
Young people nowadays are all adorable.

346
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,200
Adorable.

347
00:19:25,780 --> 00:19:26,630
What's with Erduo?

348
00:19:27,650 --> 00:19:29,350
Ye Shuwei's parents are visiting.

349
