357
00:19:47,890 --> 00:19:48,580
Right?

358
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:50,620
Zhao, anyway, please keep a close eye on it.

359
00:19:50,620 --> 00:19:51,400
I'm leaving.

360
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:52,290
I'll be waiting for you outside.

361
00:19:52,290 --> 00:19:52,850
You…

362
00:19:55,570 --> 00:19:56,780
Thank you, Zhao.

363
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:57,940
Call me if you need any help.

364
00:19:58,220 --> 00:19:58,690
Okay.

365
00:19:58,690 --> 00:19:59,240
Bye-bye.

366
00:20:03,510 --> 00:20:05,360
Your place hasn't changed a bit.

367
00:20:05,360 --> 00:20:06,660
