374
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:25,650
It is.

375
00:20:25,650 --> 00:20:28,050
Erduo made this herself.

376
00:20:28,050 --> 00:20:29,910
She's so good with her hands.

377
00:20:30,050 --> 00:20:31,180
I like it very much.

378
00:20:31,180 --> 00:20:33,570
She's as skillful as you are.

379
00:20:34,090 --> 00:20:35,220
Look at you.

380
00:20:35,220 --> 00:20:37,020
