401
00:21:20,270 --> 00:21:20,870
Okay.

402
00:21:20,870 --> 00:21:21,300
I'll walk you out.

403
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:22,160
Then we are leaving.

404
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:23,790
Purse. My Purse.

405
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:24,780
Oh, right.

406
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:28,680
Uncle and Auntie, this way.

407
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:29,410
- This way.
