421
00:22:25,700 --> 00:22:27,240
You are such a good boss.

422
00:22:27,870 --> 00:22:28,670
Then I'm going.

423
00:22:28,670 --> 00:22:30,050
Drive home safely.

424
00:22:30,050 --> 00:22:30,670
Bye-bye.

