436
00:24:11,370 --> 00:24:12,250
I'll call a cab.

437
00:24:13,010 --> 00:24:15,070
No. I just need some sleep.

438
00:24:15,070 --> 00:24:16,250
How's that gonna help?

439
00:24:16,250 --> 00:24:17,480
