441
00:24:19,990 --> 00:24:20,820
Let's go.

442
00:24:33,460 --> 00:24:35,040
Alright. We won't go to the hospital.

443
00:24:35,040 --> 00:24:36,780
How about lying down in your room then?

444
00:24:41,250 --> 00:24:42,900
Can you stand up yourself?

445
00:24:46,960 --> 00:24:50,290
Here. Put your arm around my shoulder.

446
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,270
I'll help you up. Come on.

447
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:01,320
Hang in there.

448
00:25:01,730 --> 00:25:02,960
Just hang in there.

449
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:04,730
Then we can go to bed.

450
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:13,030
I mean, hang in there,

451
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:15,960
